## ğŸš€ **What is Fedoragentic?**

Fedoragentic transforms your Fedora installation into an **AI-powered workspace** with autonomous agents that work alongside you. Built on the solid foundation of [JaKooLit's Fedora-Hyprland](https://github.com/JaKooLit/Fedora-Hyprland), we've supercharged it with intelligent agents that handle everything from system monitoring to creative tasks.

### âœ¨ **Pre-installed AI Agents**

ğŸ™ï¸ **VoiceAssist Agent** - Voice commands for system control  
ğŸ–¥ï¸ **SystemWatch Agent** - Real-time performance monitoring & optimization  
ğŸ“ **FileOrganizer Agent** - Intelligent file management and sorting  
ğŸŒ **NetGuard Agent** - Network security monitoring and threat detection  
ğŸ’» **CodeCompanion Agent** - AI-powered development assistant  
ğŸ¨ **DesktopArt Agent** - Dynamic wallpaper generation based on mood/time  
ğŸ“Š **DataViz Agent** - Automatic data visualization and reporting  
ğŸ”§ **AutoMaintenance Agent** - System cleanup and optimization  
ğŸŒ **CloudSync Agent** - Intelligent multi-cloud synchronization  
ğŸµ **AudioMood Agent** - Ambient sound generation based on workflow

### ğŸ³ **Podman-Ready Deployment**

All agents are containerized and deployable via Podman with one-command installation:

```bash
# Deploy individual agents
podman run -d --name voiceassist fedoragentic/voiceassist:latest

# Or deploy the full agent suite
./deploy-agents.sh --all
```

