## ğŸ›¡ï¸ **System Requirements**

- **OS**: Fedora 40+ (or compatible)
- **RAM**: 8GB minimum, 16GB recommended
- **Storage**: 50GB free space
- **GPU**: Any modern GPU (NVIDIA/AMD/Intel)
- **Network**: Stable internet for agent updates

